reviewText: Don't get me wrong,the dvd was good but it seemed liked there was too much narrating,c'mon do we care really about the girls likes and dislikes? anyway,it didn't ruin my enjoyment i think i liked "sexy sports special" better though.one great reason to look at Disappearing Lingerie is the fact that Angel Veil(one of the last new Juggies from the Man Show) is on it and there's extra footage of her at the end of the feature. And this dvd is becoming hard to find...
